Xconq 2 ---+++ The world in 1941;
There are five sides. You're out if you lose your capital.
The Germans win if they get 750 pts. of territory
The Commonwealth wins if they still have London on turn 600
The Japanese win on 600 pts. of territory
And the Americans win by taking Tokyo on or after turn 100
.
